00:21:14,080 --> 00:21:17,200
also for protecting human life,

45
00:21:17,200 --> 00:21:19,410
nourishing human life.

46
00:21:24,870 --> 00:21:28,410
The same weapons can be used in a wrong direction,

47
00:21:29,120 --> 00:21:30,870
but, rightly used,

48
00:21:33,200 --> 00:21:41,000
they can be dedicated for the use of God's work.

49
00:21:43,740 --> 00:21:46,540
All that is created by human beings,

50
00:21:50,950 --> 00:21:53,540
which looks apparently

51
00:21:55,410 --> 00:22:00,950
an instrument of destruction,

52
00:22:02,160 --> 00:22:06,290
but if human beings use their wisdom

53
00:22:08,080 --> 00:22:10,200
they will find out

54
00:22:10,740 --> 00:22:16,000
that all these inventions that have come to them

55
00:22:17,200 --> 00:22:23,120
from the prompting of the Unconscious,

56
00:22:23,870 --> 00:22:27,160
are for the work of God.

57
00:22:28,200 --> 00:22:30,290
All scientific research,

58
00:22:30,580 --> 00:22:32,740
everything that has been done,

59
00:22:33,330 --> 00:22:36,200
all these instruments that you have produced,

60
00:22:36,870 --> 00:22:39,740
are for the use of God.

61
00:22:40,660 --> 00:22:42,620
In a way we can say

62
00:22:42,620 --> 00:22:46,500
that human beings have worked

63
00:22:48,250 --> 00:22:53,740
to create methods as instruments,

64
00:22:56,870 --> 00:23:02,660
as social, economic, political institutions

65
00:23:07,250 --> 00:23:12,580
to advance the mechanism of God's work.

66
00:23:14,160 --> 00:23:17,160
The Unconscious has worked through human beings.

67
00:23:19,160 --> 00:23:21,830
All these institutions,

68
00:23:22,160 --> 00:23:24,410
if they are put to the right side

69
00:23:26,740 --> 00:23:32,790
of their activity and not to the hellish activity,

70
00:23:35,700 --> 00:23:39,160
they all can join together

71
00:23:42,200 --> 00:23:46,200
to complete the work of the Divine.

72
00:23:48,790 --> 00:23:55,580
Like, in the East people believe

73
00:23:56,290 --> 00:24:01,000
that God has created this beautiful body of human beings

74
00:24:01,500 --> 00:24:04,160
and it is for human beings

75
00:24:05,160 --> 00:24:13,700
to create beautiful artistic clothes to enhance the beauty

76
00:24:14,160 --> 00:24:16,200
of what God has created,

77
00:24:16,200 --> 00:24:19,740
to glorify the beauty of what God has created,

78
00:24:22,040 --> 00:24:25,910
to respect the beauty that God has created.

79
00:24:29,830 --> 00:24:32,910
And that's what has happened

80
00:24:33,910 --> 00:24:37,290
in many spheres of life, of human activities,

81
00:24:37,290 --> 00:24:40,500
and should have happened in all of them

82
00:24:40,910 --> 00:24:43,290
if they had used their wisdom.

83
00:24:50,160 --> 00:24:54,290
The question of knowledge

84
00:24:56,250 --> 00:24:58,410
that I discussed before

85
00:24:58,660 --> 00:25:01,370
is very important to understand.

86
00:25:03,830 --> 00:25:06,910
The knowledge that was forbidden

87
00:25:06,910 --> 00:25:10,000
once upon a time, such as Adam and Eve,

88
00:25:10,660 --> 00:25:14,120
has been a big problem for human beings to understand.

89
00:25:15,790 --> 00:25:19,080
It was the case when

90
00:25:19,080 --> 00:25:22,950
God created human beings first time,

91
00:25:24,620 --> 00:25:27,950
apart from the celestial beings, who were perfect,

92
00:25:30,740 --> 00:25:32,080
that He wanted to see

93
00:25:32,080 --> 00:25:34,620
if these human beings could grow

94
00:25:35,120 --> 00:25:39,950
in their population and in their awareness,

95
00:25:40,450 --> 00:25:42,410
in their innocence,

96
00:25:45,540 --> 00:25:50,410
they would become Self Realized.

97
00:25:53,410 --> 00:25:56,540
But it was an experiment,

98
00:25:57,410 --> 00:26:00,620
and the human beings failed God at that time,

99
00:26:01,540 --> 00:26:05,620
because they listened to baser promotions

100
00:26:05,870 --> 00:26:06,790
or baser prompting.

101
00:26:16,200 --> 00:26:18,410
That's how they failed

102
00:26:18,660 --> 00:26:20,660
and they lost their innocence.

103
00:26:20,740 --> 00:26:28,330
And the loss of innocence is the sin

104
00:26:29,410 --> 00:26:31,620
which was first committed,

105
00:26:32,000 --> 00:26:36,540
and that sin took a different turn

106
00:26:38,740 --> 00:26:40,540
for human beings.

107
00:26:41,080 --> 00:26:44,620
Now, that knowledge, what I've said,

108
00:26:44,620 --> 00:26:47,250
is not this real knowledge.

109
00:26:47,250 --> 00:26:51,080
That was the avidya, the artificial knowledge,

110
00:26:51,080 --> 00:26:53,870
the knowledge that "I am something,"

111
00:26:54,450 --> 00:27:00,330
that "I am the doer", the ego."

112
00:27:02,290 --> 00:27:05,870
Till the animal stage there was no ego,

113
00:27:06,120 --> 00:27:09,330
and then the ego started growing.

114
00:27:09,330 --> 00:27:12,080
We can say that's the beginning

115
00:27:12,080 --> 00:27:13,740
of the original sin:

116
00:27:13,740 --> 00:27:15,870
that "I am something.

117
00:27:15,870 --> 00:27:17,870
I am doing something."

118
00:27:17,870 --> 00:27:20,740
"It's I who can do it". All right?"

119
00:27:20,740 --> 00:27:21,910
So God said,

120
00:27:21,910 --> 00:27:25,410
"Let's see. Let's see their little courage,

121
00:27:26,620 --> 00:27:28,580
and let them decide."

122
00:27:29,540 --> 00:27:31,540
So the plans were changed,

123
00:27:32,370 --> 00:27:35,910
one had to think now that we should

124
00:27:36,160 --> 00:27:38,790
get incarnations on this earth

125
00:27:39,290 --> 00:27:41,910
to help these people, to guide them,

126
00:27:41,910 --> 00:27:44,410
to put them into a balance,

127
00:27:45,200 --> 00:27:48,910
to put them into proper understanding of dharma,

128
00:27:50,040 --> 00:27:55,700
so they keep to that balance.

129
00:27:56,120 --> 00:28:01,330
But every time this "I" refused to accept the balance.

130
00:28:02,700 --> 00:28:08,740
And this "I" goes very far from reality.

131
00:28:10,120 --> 00:28:14,870
Today also, when we come to Sahaja Yoga,

132
00:28:15,620 --> 00:28:17,330
I see people,

133
00:28:17,870 --> 00:28:20,120
they don't grow very fast.

134
00:28:20,120 --> 00:28:23,740
Because of this "I" they have questions,

135
00:28:24,620 --> 00:28:28,580
they have doubts, they have problems.

136
00:28:29,000 --> 00:28:31,200
Because of this original sin

137
00:28:32,450 --> 00:28:36,200
people cannot grow very fast.

138
00:28:37,540 --> 00:28:40,870
That, "I am the one, I am free.

139
00:28:41,370 --> 00:28:44,330
Why that? Why this?"

140
00:28:44,910 --> 00:28:47,450
Who are you to ask questions?

141
00:28:47,660 --> 00:28:49,250
Who has made you?

142
00:28:49,250 --> 00:28:51,620
Have you made yourself?

143
00:28:51,620 --> 00:28:54,450
What did you do to become a human being?

144
00:28:54,450 --> 00:28:58,790
Why this kind of egoistical behavior towards God?

145
00:28:59,250 --> 00:29:01,620
"Why God has made us? Why this thing?"

146
00:29:01,620 --> 00:29:04,330
Who are you to ask any question?

147
00:29:05,450 --> 00:29:08,200
But it is so, the questioning goes on,

148
00:29:08,200 --> 00:29:10,200
and such people are very dangerous

149
00:29:10,740 --> 00:29:12,330
for Sahaja Yoga.

150
00:29:13,410 --> 00:29:18,870
If they have to come for puja, I'm worried,

151
00:29:19,330 --> 00:29:21,870
not because anything will happen to puja,

152
00:29:21,870 --> 00:29:24,830
but because we may lose them completely.

153
00:29:24,830 --> 00:29:28,410
Such egoistical stupid people get lost.

154
00:29:28,410 --> 00:29:32,700
As a mother I have simple compassion and love for them,

155
00:29:33,700 --> 00:29:38,500
and I feel sad that they could have been saved.

156
00:29:38,740 --> 00:29:41,160
But this questioning mind of theirs

157
00:29:41,160 --> 00:29:43,040
can drown them.

158
00:29:43,410 --> 00:29:45,160
This is the basic original sin

159
00:29:45,160 --> 00:29:47,830
that human beings have created.

160
00:29:48,330 --> 00:29:49,950
Apart from that,

161
00:29:50,200 --> 00:29:53,160
we had the problem that we have come

162
00:29:53,410 --> 00:29:55,830
from the animal stage to this stage.

163
00:29:56,160 --> 00:30:03,040
So there are animal brutal conditionings within you.

164
00:30:04,330 --> 00:30:07,830
Then we have gone through other conditionings,

165
00:30:08,160 --> 00:30:13,200
which were created in the history

166
00:30:13,500 --> 00:30:15,700
by the same mister "I"

167
00:30:16,290 --> 00:30:18,200
who has started institutions,

168
00:30:19,330 --> 00:30:21,830
who started organizing religions.

169
00:30:22,080 --> 00:30:24,500
For example, take Christianity.

170
00:30:25,410 --> 00:30:28,080
Christ came here to break your ego.

171
00:30:28,500 --> 00:30:32,040
On the contrary, people built a big ego out of it.

172
00:30:32,330 --> 00:30:35,000
Now, there are some Sahaja Yogis

173
00:30:35,250 --> 00:30:37,000
who believe that

174
00:30:37,370 --> 00:30:39,660
Sahaja Yoga is a Christian Sahaja Yoga

175
00:30:39,660 --> 00:30:41,620
or a Hindu Sahaja Yoga.

176
00:30:41,910 --> 00:30:45,910
Still that lingers on, that lingers on,

177
00:30:46,450 --> 00:30:48,790
that it is a Christian Sahaja Yoga.

178
00:30:48,790 --> 00:30:51,620
"For Christians it has to be Christian Sahaja Yoga"

179
00:30:52,250 --> 00:30:55,120
for Hindus it should be a Hindu Sahaja Yoga.

180
00:30:56,250 --> 00:30:58,660
"For Muslims it is a Muslim Sahaja Yoga;

181
00:30:58,910 --> 00:31:00,250
it must relate to Islam,"

182
00:31:00,250 --> 00:31:02,500
because they can't get out of their own conditioning,

183
00:31:02,740 --> 00:31:04,120
so it must relate to that,

184
00:31:04,370 --> 00:31:06,330
it must explain everything that is there.

185
00:31:06,330 --> 00:31:08,500
They can't get out, you see?

186
00:31:08,740 --> 00:31:11,000
It could be also a Catholic Sahaja Yoga

187
00:31:11,000 --> 00:31:13,000
or a Protestant Sahaja Yoga.

188
00:31:13,000 --> 00:31:15,620
Could be even deeper than that.

189
00:31:15,620 --> 00:31:17,620
Like that, you see, it goes on.

190
00:31:17,620 --> 00:31:19,540
So, you pull Sahaja Yoga

191
00:31:19,540 --> 00:31:21,080
into your own categories,

192
00:31:21,080 --> 00:31:23,660
into your own small little cups.

193
00:31:24,250 --> 00:31:26,500
But it's just the other way round.

194
00:31:26,500 --> 00:31:30,740
Sahaja Yoga is the ocean, is a universal thing,

195
00:31:30,740 --> 00:31:32,330
it is a MahaYoga.

196
00:31:32,580 --> 00:31:34,910
"It is not meant for Christians, Hindus, Muslims" or anything;

197
00:31:34,910 --> 00:31:39,540
it is meant for human beings as they were.

198
00:31:40,620 --> 00:31:43,250
Have you got animals who are Christians,

199
00:31:43,250 --> 00:31:45,200
Hindus or Muslims?

200
00:31:45,450 --> 00:31:48,200
This all comes because of the original sin only,

201
00:31:48,450 --> 00:31:50,620
that we are something, we are Christians,

202
00:31:50,620 --> 00:31:52,910
we are Hindus, we are Muslims.

203
00:31:52,910 --> 00:31:55,660
In Sahaja Yoga, one has to understand

204
00:31:55,660 --> 00:31:59,080
that all the rivers, whether it is the River Ganges

205
00:31:59,620 --> 00:32:01,370
or the River Yamuna

206
00:32:01,740 --> 00:32:03,540
or it is the River Thames

207
00:32:03,740 --> 00:32:05,620
or River Danube, any river,

208
00:32:05,870 --> 00:32:09,580
that all of them flow into the same ocean and become the ocean.

209
00:32:10,200 --> 00:32:12,040
They say that when all the rivers

210
00:32:12,040 --> 00:32:13,790
flow in the River Ganges,

211
00:32:14,040 --> 00:32:17,870
they are all called as Surasari, means "the River of the Gods."

212
00:32:17,870 --> 00:32:20,580
No more people call them by the different names

213
00:32:20,580 --> 00:32:24,040
of the tributaries that are there.

214
00:32:24,040 --> 00:32:26,910
In the same way, Sahaja Yoga is the ocean.

215
00:32:27,200 --> 00:32:28,370
You cannot name it.

216
00:32:28,660 --> 00:32:33,000
Do not try to find its identity with other things.

217
00:32:33,000 --> 00:32:35,250
If you start doing that, then your mind

218
00:32:35,580 --> 00:32:40,250
will start becoming that small little cup.

219
00:32:40,740 --> 00:32:44,540
And moreover, if you are coming from some organized religion,

220
00:32:44,540 --> 00:32:47,450
it is very important to understand that organized religions

221
00:32:47,700 --> 00:32:50,410
make your cup even stronger, it doesn't dissolve.

222
00:32:50,700 --> 00:32:52,040
If it is a disorganised religion,

223
00:32:52,040 --> 00:32:55,200
then it is a cup of earthenware,

224
00:32:55,450 --> 00:32:57,040
which can dissolve into this ocean.

225
00:32:57,290 --> 00:32:59,740
But if it is a solid, nice porcelain,

226
00:33:01,160 --> 00:33:04,450
Meisonn, there is no possibility.

227
00:33:04,740 --> 00:33:07,620
Then you are adhering to all that conditioning,

228
00:33:08,290 --> 00:33:11,870
all that solidness, and then it's very difficult.

229
00:33:12,160 --> 00:33:14,450
All the time you have to bring in Christ

230
00:33:14,740 --> 00:33:16,700
or you have to bring in Mohammad

231
00:33:16,950 --> 00:33:18,580
or you have to bring in Zoroaster,

232
00:33:18,870 --> 00:33:22,700
or someone like that who should be there to guide you.

233
00:33:23,410 --> 00:33:25,740
Now your guidance is your Spirit,

234
00:33:25,740 --> 00:33:27,330
which is unlimited,

235
00:33:27,330 --> 00:33:29,540
so you don't have to bring any one of Them.

236
00:33:29,540 --> 00:33:30,950
They are all within you.

237
00:33:31,200 --> 00:33:33,000
They are all part and parcel of you.

238
00:33:33,250 --> 00:33:36,120
But to stick on to one person is again

239
00:33:36,120 --> 00:33:39,120
a sign that you are not expanding.

240
00:33:39,580 --> 00:33:41,950
You know that you are all.

241
00:33:41,950 --> 00:33:44,330
You have got Shri Krishna within you, who is awakened,

242
00:33:44,580 --> 00:33:46,040
you have got Christ within you,

243
00:33:46,410 --> 00:33:48,740
you have got Ganesha within you,

244
00:33:49,080 --> 00:33:50,950
you have got Brahmadeva within you,

245
00:33:51,290 --> 00:33:53,290
and you have got Mohammad within you.

246
00:33:53,580 --> 00:33:54,910
"And you have got all of Them:

247
00:33:55,200 --> 00:33:57,040
Moses, everyone, within you"

248
00:33:57,330 --> 00:34:00,080
so how can you be identified with one person?

249
00:34:00,500 --> 00:34:02,950
The reason is, you are still conditioned,

250
00:34:03,290 --> 00:34:06,910
and you want to drag it into your own conditioning.

251
00:34:08,290 --> 00:34:14,500
So try to bring it at a position where there is no conditioning.

252
00:34:14,500 --> 00:34:17,330
We can see our conditioning worse works so much

253
00:34:18,080 --> 00:34:20,540
with our style because,

254
00:34:20,870 --> 00:34:30,790
as human beings, we have a habit of forming a closed sect,

255
00:34:31,120 --> 00:34:32,370
"whether it is ourselves,

256
00:34:32,660 --> 00:34:36,660
first we close ourselves as "I." "I am XYZ."

257
00:34:37,000 --> 00:34:39,790
Then we can club together as,

258
00:34:40,200 --> 00:34:45,790
say, "We are, say, people who use forks and knives".

259
00:34:45,790 --> 00:34:48,330
There could be people who just use

260
00:34:48,330 --> 00:34:50,700
the fork and knives this way can be clubbed together,

261
00:34:50,700 --> 00:34:53,870
and the others who use this way can be another way.

262
00:34:54,160 --> 00:34:55,580
See, it goes on like that,

263
00:34:55,830 --> 00:34:57,410
all kinds of stupidity

264
00:34:57,620 --> 00:34:59,330
that human beings have to club together.

265
00:34:59,330 --> 00:35:01,910
All right, use the way you like, it makes no difference.

266
00:35:02,160 --> 00:35:05,700
You eat the same food, it digests the same way, and it works the same.

267
00:35:05,950 --> 00:35:08,080
But as far as the outside is concerned,

268
00:35:08,330 --> 00:35:09,950
when it comes to human activity,

269
00:35:09,950 --> 00:35:12,000
they will use the fork and spoon in a different way,

270
00:35:12,000 --> 00:35:14,200
somebody will use their hands, fingers,

